Budget Buddy is your ultimate financial sidekick, designed to simplify your money management journey. With Budget Buddy, keeping track of your expenses and income is a piece of cake !

📝 Easy Expense Tracking: Add, categorize, and monitor your expenses and income effortlessly. Think of Budget Buddy as your digital financial diary, always there to help you stay on top of your spending.

📈 Visual Insights: Dive into colorful charts and graphs to gain valuable insights into your financial habits. With Budget Buddy, understanding your spending patterns has never been easier!

💼 Dashboard Overview: Get a bird's eye view of your finances with our intuitive dashboard. Set monthly budgets, track your progress, and keep tabs on your financial health with ease.

🔍Outstanding Navigation: Explore different sections of the app effortlessly with our user-friendly sidebar navigation. From transaction categories to detailed reports, everything is just a click away.

🔒 Secure and Accurate: Rest assured, your data is safe with Budget Buddy. Our robust validation ensures that every expense and transaction is accurately recorded and securely stored.

💡 Future Updates: But wait, there's more! i am constantly working on new features to make Budget Buddy even better. Stay tuned for exciting updates!

💻 Powered by Technology: Built using technologies like C#,APIs, Styling, MVC framework, Entity Framework Core, Scripts, and SQLDatabase Functions to store safely every user's Data , Budget Buddy offers a seamless user experience with a sleek design.
